{"type": "article", "id": 10170, "title": "「 儿童节可以准备起来了」之 Ted 小熊玩偶", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-29T07:20:48Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 3, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235626aZuKFAID0f2t7niM.png", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t即将上映的《Ted 2》和 Medicom Toy 联手推出了一款 400% Bearbrick 玩偶，这只小熊身高 280mm，全身棕色，而且特别可爱地搭配了一条 Ted 小熊特色的小尾巴。目前售价 65 美元，已经开始接受预定，不过将会在 8 月才开始运送。此外 Medicom Toy 还和《Transformers》等推出了联名玩偶，<a href=\"http://www.medicomtoy.co.jp/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看更多详细信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235624rhRLtJzwHfscp8G9.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.75462963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235624gwf4xhD79bN8krJq.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71481481\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235625dz7CNi9r1QjGI6mn.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.79444444\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235625EwrbIBodYSHn9G1V.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.76666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}